## 🧰 Installation & Setup

1. Download the latest `.exe` from the Releases page above.  
2. Run the installer or open the portable `.exe`.  
3. Log in or paste your AI API key if prompted.  
4. Open your chat app (WhatsApp, Discord, etc.) and place the window where you want.  
5. In AI Message Responder:
   - Click “Select Chat Area” and draw a box around the messages.[page:26]  
   - Optionally select the input box area if required.  
6. Click “Start Auto‑Responder”.

You can stop it anytime using the **Stop** button or by closing the app.

