## ❗ Important Notes

- This tool reads only the part of the screen you select, but you are still responsible for what is sent under your account.[page:26]  
- Use it respectfully on servers and chats that allow automation.  
- Check each platform’s Terms of Service to make sure you are not breaking any rules.

